sentences.sentence: By the time we had made landfall the boat looked ten years older!
sentences.translation: 等到我们登陆时，这艘船看似已老了10年！

sentences.sentence: After three weeks they made landfall on the coast of Ireland.
sentences.translation: 三个星期之后，他们登上了爱尔兰的海岸。

sentences.sentence: Ike made landfall in Texas more than four months ago.
sentences.translation: 艾克四个多月以前在德克·萨斯登陆。
